### ===========================
### Admin User Management
### ===========================

### List users (default)
# Fetches the first page of users with default sorting.
GET {{host}}/api/admin/users
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### List users (paginated)
# Fetches the second page of users with a page size of 10.
GET {{host}}/api/admin/users?page=1&size=10
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### List users (search by username or email)
# Searches users whose username or email contains the given query.
GET {{host}}/api/admin/users?search=john
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### List users (filter by status)
# Fetches only users with BANNED status.
GET {{host}}/api/admin/users?status=BANNED
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### List users (sorted by username ascending)
# Fetches users sorted by username in ascending order.
GET {{host}}/api/admin/users?sort=username&direction=ASC
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### List users (combined filters)
# Searches for active users matching "pirate", sorted by last login.
GET {{host}}/api/admin/users?search=pirate&status=ACTIVE&sort=lastLogin&direction=DESC&page=0&size=20
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Get user details
# Fetches detailed information about a specific user including profile, preferences, and statistics.
GET {{host}}/api/admin/users/{{user_id}}
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Ban user (permanent)
# Permanently bans a user with a reason. Deactivates all their active ads.
POST {{host}}/api/admin/users/{{user_id}}/ban
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "reason": "Repeated policy violations and fraudulent listings"
}

### Ban user (temporary)
# Temporarily bans a user until the specified timestamp (epoch micros). Deactivates all their active ads.
POST {{host}}/api/admin/users/{{user_id}}/ban
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "reason": "Inappropriate content in listings - 7-day ban",
  "bannedUntil": 1750000000000000
}

### Unban user
# Lifts the ban from a user, restoring their account to active status.
# Note: Their ads are NOT automatically reactivated — the user must do that manually.
POST {{host}}/api/admin/users/{{user_id}}/unban
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Get ban history
# Fetches the full ban history for a user, including both active and past bans.
GET {{host}}/api/admin/users/{{user_id}}/bans
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
